On the Evolution of Ecology and Evolutionary Biology
This code and data replicates the revolutions analysis found in On Revolutions (Leroi et al. 2020) for all ecology and evolutionary biology papers present in the JSTOR archives from 1900-2010. It contains:  (1) a data file with all the data used in the study (2) the Foote Novelty algorithm and plot functions implemented in R (3) the persistence estimator (rho) which is written in Stan the FN code is required to run this as the R file calls the Stan file (4) the Haldane Rate Analysis algorithm and plot functions implemented in R.}
